description:
Amit Tishler is the president of 10 Forward Productions, Inc. He is animator, writer and director with Master of Fine Art from MCAD. He specializes in animation, concept art, and character design for both TV and games. Amit is an award-winning film maker. His films were screened in various film festivals including: The Philadelphia Film and Animation Festival, The Manhattan Film Festival, Canada International Film Festival, New York City International Film Festival, Animaldicoados, and more.

Amit has had the privilege to work on projects for clients like Adult Swim, Comedy Central, Nickelodeon, Hallmark as well as many other exceptional studios and organizations across the country and abroad.
name: Amit Tishler

deck: Troy Vevasis is a comic creator and writer. He is the writer of Vincent Price Presents: In The Shadows #1 published by Storm Comics.  He is the creator and writer of the Mr. Crypt series published by Alterna Comics!  He is also the creator and writer of Fredrick the Frost Gnome published by WP Comics and The Diamond Star published by Tenacious Comics! His comics "The Harvest" and "The Duel" were included in Indie Comics Magazine #9 and #10.
name: Troy Vevasis
